00:29:16.680 --> 00:29:30.520
at the frequency omega
1, which is faster

00:29:30.520 --> 00:29:31.625
than the Larmor frequency.

00:29:37.850 --> 00:29:41.150
And the question
is now what will

00:29:41.150 --> 00:29:44.590
happen to the spin or
the magnetic moment.

00:29:44.590 --> 00:29:48.810
I explained to you
that on a resonance,

00:29:48.810 --> 00:29:54.690
the magnetic moment was
just flipping over, rotating

00:29:54.690 --> 00:29:59.040
precessing at the
