00:32:03.692 --> 00:32:04.686
The yellow.

00:32:09.670 --> 00:32:11.090
This projector has a problem.

00:32:14.000 --> 00:32:20.280
So now same question
as before, but instead

00:32:20.280 --> 00:32:23.980
of driving the system with a
