00:32:23.980 --> 00:32:27.170
than the Larmor frequency,
we are driving it

00:32:27.170 --> 00:32:29.330
with a smaller frequency.

00:32:29.330 --> 00:32:32.770
Is now the response of
the magnetic moment,

00:32:32.770 --> 00:32:36.730
the effective precession
frequency, larger, smaller,

00:32:36.730 --> 00:32:40.430
or the same as the Rabi
