00:58:51.210 --> 00:58:53.150
That's a standard situation.

00:58:53.150 --> 00:58:56.640
Or we always want to have
quantization axis, which

00:58:56.640 --> 00:58:58.840
is given with the
z-axis as defined

00:58:58.840 --> 00:59:01.600
by the static magnetic
field, but it's only

00:59:01.600 --> 00:59:03.820
defined by the
static magnetic field

00:59:03.820 --> 00:59:05.870
if the transverse
field is not much

00:59:05.870 --> 00:59:07.670
larger than the static
field, otherwise,

00:59:07.670 --> 00:59:09.978
we are talking about a
