00:59:12.820 --> 00:59:17.710
And let me just assume
to be specific we later

00:59:17.710 --> 00:59:20.100
discuss what happens
if it's not the case.

00:59:20.100 --> 00:59:25.020
We assume that we start with
a frequency omega, which

00:59:25.020 --> 00:59:27.457
